  <description><![CDATA[<p>Our homely and traditional 'Small &amp; Friendly' hotels in the Arlberg ski area offer comfortable accommodation on a half board basis and represent excellent value for money and immediate swift access onto the huge Arlberg ski area, with its 280km of piste. Situated in next-door villages to St. Anton, the main Nasserein gondola stop is not more than 10 minutes' ride away on the regular free ski bus.</p>]]></description>
